Various tooling for Xbox Development

amd_cpu_enum.c:
Prints the following:
Vendor
CPU
Cores
Threads
CPU Feature Flags
AMD Cache Leaves
Cache Sharing Topology
Raw Leaves
Hypervisor max leaf
Hypervisor vendor
HV interface
HV features EAX
HV features EBX
Max standard leaf
Max extended leaf
Cache Sizes
Extended topology info

nt_krnl_xhook.c:
Prints loaded kernel modules

tsc_enum.c:
Prints approx freq for each core


wdp_rest.py:
A wrapper for the rest api

Use python wdp_rest.py --help for more info
